    <item>
      <title>报告发现，毛伊岛火灾是由公用电线断裂引起的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/maui-fire-caused-by-broken-utility-power-lines-report-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[毛伊岛消防部门表示，去年，夏威夷电力工业公司重新接通断裂的公共设施线路时产生的火花点燃了未维护的干燥植被，从而引发了火灾，烧毁了毛伊岛历史悠久的拉海纳镇。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/maui-fire-caused-by-broken-utility-power-lines-report-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 22:30:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东供应风险主导油价连续第三天上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价连续第三天上涨，因为交易商评估了中东的供应风险，预计以色列将在本周早些时候对伊朗发动导弹袭击后对伊朗进行报复性打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 22:16:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
