    <item>
      <title>芝加哥金融委员会推进 15 亿美元债券再融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/chicago-finance-committee-advances-1-5-billion-bond-refinancing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥市议会财政委员会通过了一项 15 亿美元的债券提案，用于再融资债务，这是市长布兰登·约翰逊为弥补美国第三大城市连续赤字所做的努力之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/chicago-finance-committee-advances-1-5-billion-bond-refinancing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 21:47:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
